posts.text: 王者荣耀在周年庆更新游戏版本的时候，进行了大型的改动，新版功能让玩家赞不绝口，但是我拿buff的配音引起了大批玩家吐槽，确实是太难听了，网友每天在策划的微博下反馈刷屏，可能策划自己也觉得太难听，受不了了，终于表示要将我拿BUFF这段语音修改。 王者荣耀配音修改 王者荣耀在10月23日正式更新了S9赛季与全新版本”峡谷起源“。本次改动相当之大，新的模式，新的游戏机制以及全新的地图优化等，新版本的王者荣耀都让玩家赞不绝口。 不过，这其中当然也有一些瑕疵，通过大量玩家反馈，最让玩家无法接受的一点，就是游戏中”我拿BUFF，谢谢“这句话，许多玩家表示听到全新的配音后，整个人都不好了。小编每次听到这句话，都感觉像是在说我拿包袱。 强烈要求王者荣耀官方将”我拿BUFF，谢谢“换成之前的配音，不然每次听到这个声音，真心不想给队友让红BUFF。网友们也在王者荣耀策划的微博下情愿留言。希望能看到大家的心声，快点改掉这个恶心的配音。 终于，在大家的呼声中，王者荣耀策划Donny决定改掉这个让人不舒服的配音。 各位小伙伴对于这句话印象如何呢？新版本还有哪些需要整改的地方，不如说出来讨论一下。 这就是小编为大家带来的王者荣耀我拿buff语音修改的相关信息，希望可以帮助到您！

posts.text:
天竞点金：11.7凌晨黄金原油一路暴涨，你被套单了吗？
导读：有时候，其实大家对市场的技术分析都是正确的，但是总是会出现一点误差，要不就是价格没到位，没有及时进入市场，要不就是单子刚被扫损之后，价格却又反弹了。这其实归根究底就是对市场缺少了一种盘感。长期接触交易的专业分析师或者投资老手都知道，市场经常会出现诱多或者诱空的信号，以及一些技术骗线，而很多时候，并不是你没有分析正确整个行情，只是你没有应对这种突发状况的经验。我们称这种经验为盘感！像我自己，我一般常用的技巧是，当市场出现一个强支撑位有反弹的可能时，我并不会因为其跌破了，就认为市场走坏了，我会关注其还能否重新站上这个支撑位，如果没有站上，我是不会进场的。但是如果从新站上，那么则多单进场。这个技巧虽然不是很复杂，但是却很实用！
黄金午夜暴涨解读：
昨日，纽约联储公开在官网上发文称，美国纽约联储主席威廉·杜德利预计将在2018年中期退休，委员会正寻找继承者，落实了此前传闻。美联储主席耶伦随后表示，杜德利为美联储政策作出了重大贡献。一场颠覆美联储的高层“大换血”行动正在迅速展开。消息公布后，美债收益率曲线触及10年来最平程度。黄金价格短线激增，并迅速冲高至1282美元。对此，天竞认为，这不仅是杜德利提前退休带来的恐慌指数上涨，还有沙特组织的反腐风暴，所带来的避险情绪推升。亦是刺激了机构进行大量买盘，进而推动金价的上涨。
原油行情分析：
目前朝鲜方面的局势也并没有完全的消退，周末也有韩国民众举行了示威，反对战争，也希望通过和平的方式解决朝鲜局势，而韩国也表示，是愿意支援朝鲜的，不过是需要禁止朝鲜的挑衅行为，美国也同样的表示了此观点，但是朝鲜认为自己研究是试射是正确的，不过目前虽然有谈判的意向，但是还是需要重点关注这方面的动态。
美原油出口量的不断扩大，美WTI原油和ICE布伦特原油价格之间的价差不断扩大，增加国际对美原油的需求，美原油价格继续上涨。产量的上升使美EIA公布的数据报告显示，原油和汽油库存下降超过预期，而馏分油的降幅低于预期。美原油库存下降约240万桶，比预期的180万桶减少了更多。由于市场对OPEC的减产协议将被延长的预期，使原油价格得到了支撑。
原油技术面：
原油自突破52.8一线，就形成了连续上涨走势，周线连续四连阳的多头排列走势，大结构的上涨形态已经完成，多头走势继续蔓延，那么顺势而为就很重要，并且目前突破年内高点55.2上方，周线级别波段62.5-26反弹的76.4的位置位于54一线，目前站在54一线上方运行，本周操作上仍然以54上方逢低多为主，周线级别的突破看涨形态，日线上周五收于55.2上方，所有形态以及指标同步看涨，那么短线回落仍然以多为主，今日早盘跳空高开高走，短线回补缺口后有望继续走高，综合来看，日内白盘关注上方56整数关口压力，下方关注55.2前期高点支撑，短线继续看涨思路不变！
黄金后市怎么看？
相信关注了天竞文章的朋友都知道，我一直在黄金文章中写到金价深陷1263-1281区间震荡，只有打破1263或是1281的压制，才会有上升空间。而现在来看，已然是突破了1281美元的压制，那是不是就可以做多了呢？我只能告诉你，激进者可以做，稳健者可以等回踩1281再做。毕竟日线级别三角形形态刚刚打破，还是存在着假突破的可能。
黄金分析及日内操作策略：

posts.author: Jianta Maya (noreply@blogger.com)
posts.title: Schema Migration - Database Migration Tools
posts.text:
In software engineering, schema migration (also database migration , database change management ) refers to the management of incremental, reversible changes to relational datab ase schemas. A schema migration is performed on a database whenever it is necessary to update or revert that database's schema to some newer or older version.
Migrations are performed programmatically by using a schema migration tool . When invoked with a specified desired schema version, the tool automates the successive application or reversal of an appropriate sequence of schema changes until it is brought to the desired state.
Most schema migration tools aim to minimize the impact of schema changes on any existing data in the database. Despite this, preservation of data in general is not guaranteed because schema changes such as the deletion of a database column can destroy data (i.e. all values stored under that column for all rows in that table are deleted). Instead, the tools help to preserve the meaning of the data or to reorganize existing data to meet new requirements. Since meaning of the data often cannot be encoded, the configuration of the tools usually needs manual intervention.


History of Open Source Implementations 

source : cloudacademy.com 
2005-Mar-1 Implementation in Ruby on Rails 0.10.1, uses DSL and/or SQL. https://github.com/rails/rails/commit/eac7cf0b0608132673220d9045b8ff51dc0804e1#diff-8d3c44120f7b67ff79e2fbe6a40d0ad6 2006-Oct-16 Version 0.5 of Liquibase (first LGPL). For Java, uses XML. https://github.com/liquibase/liquibase/commit/836043ef45c82aeda5ffec42c062acf5edcfc4e0 2010-Abr-20 First implementation of Flyway for Java, see https://flywaydb.org/blog/flyway-turns-3.html Risks and benefits 

source : www.mysql.com 
Schema migration allows for fixing mistakes and adapting the data as requirements change. They are an essential part of software evolution, especially in agile environments (see below).
Applying a schema migration to a production database is always a risk. Development and test databases tend to be smaller and cleaner. The data in them is better understood or, if everything else fails, the amount of data is small enough for a human to process. Production databases are usually huge, old and full of surprises. The surprises can come from many sources:
Corrupt data that was written by old versions of the software and not cleaned properly Implied dependencies in the data which no one knows about anymore People directly changing the database without using the designated tools Bugs in the schema migration tools Mistakes in assumptions how data should be migrated For these reasons, the migration process needs a high level of discipline, thorough testing and a sound backup strategy.
Schema migration in agile software development 

source : www.iri.com 
When developing software applications backed by a database, developers typically develop the application source code in tandem with an evolving database schema. The code typically has rigid expectations of what columns, tables and constraints are present in the database schema whenever it needs to interact with one, so only the version of database schema against which the code was developed is considered fully compatible with that version of source code.
In software testing, while developers may mock the presence of a compatible database system for unit testing, any level of testing higher than this (e.g. integration testing or system testing) it is common for developers to test their application against a local or remote test database schematically compatible with the version of source code under test. In advanced applications, the migration itself can be subject to migration testing.
With schema migration technology, data models no longer need to be fully designed up-front, and are more capable of being adapted with changing project requirements throughout the software development lifecycle.
Relation to revision control systems Teams of software developers usually use version control systems to manage and collaborate on changes made to versions of source code. Different developers can develop on divergent, relatively older or newer branches of the same source code to make changes and additions during development.
Supposing that the software under development interacts with a database, every version of the source code can be associated with at least one database schema with which it is compatible.
Under good software testing practice, schema migrations can be performed on test databases to ensure that their schema is compatible to the source code. To streamline this process, a schema migration tool is usually invoked as a part of an automated software build as a prerequisite of the automated testing phase.
Schema migration tools can be said to solve versioning problems for database schemas just as version control systems solve versioning problems for source code. In practice, many schema migration tools actually rely on a textual representation of schema changes (such as files containing SQL statements) such that the version history of schema changes can effectively be stored alongside program source code within VCS. This approach ensures that the information necessary to recover a compatible database schema for a particular code branch is recoverable from the source tree itself. Another benefit of this approach is the handling of concurrent conflicting schema changes; developers may simply use their usual text-based conflict resolution tools to reconcile differences.
Relation to schema evolution Schema migration tooling could be seen as a facility to track the history of an evolving schema.
Advantages Developers no longer need to remove the entire test database in order to create a new test database from scratch (e.g. using schema creation scripts from DDL generation tools). Further, if generation of test data costs a lot of time, developers can avoid regenerating test data for small, non-destructive changes to the schema.

Nov 06 2017 
LONDON: Everton defender Michael Keane was called up on Monday to replace injured Tottenham Hotspur forward Dele Alli in the England squad for friendlies against Germany and Brazil this month. 
Alli has been ruled out after he sustained a hamstring injury during last week’s Champions League victory over Real Madrid. 
Tottenham team mates Harry Kane and Harry Winks, along with Chelsea defender Gary Cahill, will undergo late fitness tests, the Football Association said. 
“Keane has now been added to the group of players due to report to St. 
George’s Park today, ahead of the upcoming double-header at Wembley Stadium,” the FA said in a statement. 
The 24-year-old has a chance to earn his fifth England cap after returning from a leg infection during Everton’s 3-2 comeback win over Watford. England host Germany on Friday and meet Brazil four days later.

posts.title: 고흥유자농장 무농약유자 재배합니다. 유자주문하세요 :)
posts.text:
고창장수베리가 소개합니다. 고흥유자농장 무농약유자 재배합니다. 유자주문하세요 :) 1시간 전 URL 복사 본문 기타 기능 번역보기 http://blog.naver.com/gnwlstn12/221134655367 오늘 벌써 입동이라고 하네요 .
날씨가 꽤나 쌀쌀해 진것이 조금만 있으면 진짜 겨울이 될것같네요.
이맘때 수확이 들어가는게 유자인데요.
전국 유자의 최대생산지 고흥유자를 소개드릴려구요.
유자는 11월 초중순 경부터 수확이 이루어지는데요.
노랗게 색깔이 예쁜 유자는 향도 정말 좋잖아요.
겨울철에 청을 담아 따뜻하게 한잔씩 먹고 하면 너무 좋아요.
저도 유자차를 정말 좋아하다보니 자주 먹게 되더라구요.
다른 과일도 물론 친환경농법이 중요하지만
특히나 유자는 껍질까지 사용하는 과일이기때문에 무엇보다도 친환경농법으로 재배한지가 중요해요.
제가 소개드리는 유자농장은 친환경농법으로 재배한 무농약 유자를 재배하고있어요.
그러니 껍질까지도 안심하고 쓸수 있죠.
무농약 유자이다보니 일반 유자에 비해서는 빛깔이조금 옅기도하고,
모양이 조금 덜예쁠수는 있는데요.
무농약 유자이기 때문에 보이는 모습이기 때문에 상품에는 전혀 문제가 없답니다.
www.sunnyyuja.com
고흥햇살유자 전체상품목록 바로가기 본문 바로가기 로그인 회원가입 장바구니 마이페이지v 고객센터v 고흥유자 5kg 무농약 (35~40과)_2017년11월수확, 비선별 38,000원 380원 (1%) 고흥유자 5kg 특대 35~40과 배송비 : 무료 고흥유자 10kg 무농약 (70~80과)_2017년11월수확, 비선별 70,000원 700원 (1%) 배송비 : 무료 고흥유자 5kg 못난이_무농약, 2017년 11월 수확 예약발송 30,000원 300원 (1%) 맑은 바람, 따스한 햇살을 품은 고흥 유자 배송비 : 무료 NATIVE 유기농 황설탕 5 www.sunnyyuja.com 고흥이 바다와 인접하고 있고 일조량이 좋은 지역이다보니
일조량과 바다에서 불어오는 해풍때문에
타지역의 유자보다 당도가 좋게 나온다하더라구요.
그러다보니 전국에서도 고흥유자가 정말 유명하구요.
아시는 분이 하는 고흥유자농장인데 , 벌써 30년이 넘으시도록 하고계신데,
그 세월에서 배워온 노하우와 경험은 무시할수 없더라구요.
친환경농법도 주변에서 가장 먼저 준비해서 시작하셨다하니
친환경농법에서도 노하우가 대단하세요.
지금 한창 이제 수확이 되기 시작할철이라 유자주문을 받으신다고 하네요.
5kg, 10kg 단위로 주문가능하구요.
저도 철마다 받아먹는데, 5kg해서 유자청 담아놓으면 한해는 두고 잘 먹게 되네요.
시중에 파는거보다 직접 담아먹다보니 더 좋구요.
올겨울 향기좋고 맛좋은 유자청 준비하실분들께 추천드리고싶네요.
무농약 고흥햇살유자농장 이에요 :)

posts.title: Así será el nuevo misterio de la Hermandad de Jesucristo Resucitado
posts.text:
La Hermandad de Jesucirsto Resucitado ha proyectado el grupo escultórico que representará su paso de misterio, presidido por Jesucristo Resucitado. La persona encargada de realizar el proyecto es José María Leal Bernáldez, autor de imágenes sagradas como la Entrada Triunfal de Pozoblanco o la Coronación de Espinas de Campillos, entre muchas otras. 

El pasado 28 de octubre se presentó el boceto del grupo escultórico en la Parroquia de Nuestra Señora de Montserrat de la capital almeriense. El propio imaginero presentó su obra a los allí presentes, entre los que destacaban los miembros de la Junta de Gobierno de la propia Cofradía, así como la presidenta de la Agrupación de Hermandades y Cofradías de Almería. Está previsto que la imagen de Jesús Resucitado sea bendecida en el año 2019, y el resto de imágenes secundarias que pueden observarse en las fotografías de la galería que citamos en esta noticia, se ejecuten en los posteriores años. 

En el misterio se representa el pasaje evangélico de la Resurrección de Jesús según San Mateo, en el que se describe cómo el Ángel del Señor bajó del cielo y dijo a María Magdalena y las otras mujeres: “Vosotras no temáis. Sé que buscáis a Jesús el crucificado. No está aquí; ha resucitado como había dicho. Acercaos a ver el lugar donde yacía. Después id corriendo a anunciar a los discípulos que ha resucitado y que irá por delante a Galilea; allí lo veréis. Éste es mi mensaje”, así como el posterior encuentro de Jesús con ellas y les dijo: “No temáis; id a avisar a mis hermanos que vayan a Galilea, donde me verán”. 

Por lo tanto, en el misterio se entrelazan estas dos escenas, el encuentro de las mujeres con el Ángel del Señor y, posteriormente, con el propio Jesús ya Resucitado. En la escena destaca el intercambio de miradas entre Jesús y María Magdalena, pieza fundamental para entender la Pasión de Cristo, también en la Resurrección ya que, como se ha indicado anteriormente, en las sagradas escrituras María Magdalena es anunciadora de la Resurrección de Jesús. 
Fuente:  http://www.gentedepaz.es/
